Class DrillSideways.DrillSidewaysResult

    DrillSideways

    public static class DrillSideways.DrillSidewaysResult
extends Object
    Represents the returned result from a drill sideways search. Note that if you called DrillSideways.search(DrillDownQuery, Collector, FacetSearchParams), then hits will be null.
